<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5"> صحيح:</span> خ <span class="c2">(٣٧٨٥)</span> , م <span class="c2">(٧/ ١٧٤)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ أَبُو حَاتِمٍ رَضِيَ اللَّهُ عَنْهُ:</span> مُعَوَّلُ هَذِهِ الْأَخْبَارِ كُلِّهَا عَلَى <span class="c2">(مِنْ)</span> فحُذِفَ <span class="c2">(مِنْ)</span> منها<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>